FRAGTrack™ is a state-of-the-art fragmentation
measurement tool that uses advanced machine
vision technologies to enable automated post-blast
measurement and analysis. Available in both conveyor and shovel-based configurations, FRAGTrack™ delivers online fragmentation data, benchmarks and insights needed to ensure sustainable and cost-effective improvements in blast performance at your operations. To learn more about the FRAGTrack™ and how it can support your operations today, please contact your local Orica representative orica.com/FRAGTrack